     <p class="card-text">•	Areas
<br>•	Averages
<br>•	Mensuration
<br>•	Simplification
<br>•	Probability
<br>•	Partnership
<br>•	Boats and Streams
<br>•	Time and Distance
<br>•	Time and Work
<br>•	Simple Interest
<br>•	Compound Interest
<br>•	Ratios and Proportions
<br>•	Problems on Trains
     
     <h5 class="card-title"><b>Reasoning Section Syllabus:</b></h5>
     <p class="card-text">•	Analogies
<br>•	Directions
<br>•	Classification
<br>•	Blood Relations
<br>•	Critical Reasoning
<br>•	Venn Diagrams
